    Update sprint status, safety invariant documentation, and tests
    
    - Updated last_updated timestamp in sprint-status.yaml.
    - Changed development status of story 1-15 to 'review'.
    - Modified allowed fields in safety-invariant CI gates documentation to include hashed repository-relative path.
    - Updated tests to reflect changes in safety invariant gates, including assertions for categories and last evaluated dates.
    - Adjusted test fixtures to use synthetic URLs and updated quarantine controls.
    - Enhanced safety channel inventory to reflect prerequisite drift diagnostics and added last evaluated timestamps.
    - Updated run-safety-invariant-gates.ps1 script to ensure the safety test assembly is present when skipping restore/build.

